</tr><tr><td style="text-align:right;font-size:115%;padding-top: 0.6em;"><div class="plainlinks hlist navbar mini"><ul><li class="nv-view"><a href="/wiki/Template:Hindu_scriptures" class="mw-redirect" title="Template:Hindu scriptures"><abbr title="View this template">v</abbr></a></li><li class="nv-talk"><a href="/wiki/Template_talk:Hindu_scriptures" class="mw-redirect" title="Template talk:Hindu scriptures"><abbr title="Discuss this template">t</abbr></a></li><li class="nv-edit"><a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Hindu_scriptures&amp;action=edit"><abbr title="Edit this template">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>
<p><b>Samhita</b> literally means "put together, joined, union",<sup id="cite_ref-monier_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-monier-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> a "collection",<sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-2">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and "a methodically, rule-based combination of text or verses".<sup id="cite_ref-monier_1-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-monier-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <i>Samhita</i> also refers to the most ancient layer of text in the <a href="/wiki/Veda" class="mw-redirect" title="Veda">Vedas</a>, consisting of <a href="/wiki/Mantra" title="Mantra">mantras</a>, hymns, prayers, <a href="/wiki/Litany" title="Litany">litanies</a> and <a href="/wiki/Benediction" title="Benediction">benedictions</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-jl_3-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-jl-3">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>
</p><p>Parts of <i>Vedic Samhitas</i> constitute the oldest living part of <a href="/wiki/Hinduism" title="Hinduism">Hindu</a> tradition.<sup id="cite_ref-jl_3-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-jl-3">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc" role="navigation" aria-labelledby="mw-toc-heading"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2 id="mw-toc-heading">Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
